channel.title: How do i change ALCHEMING item prices!
channel.description:
i have project insanity evoscape source and i have a noted item that alchs for mroe then what is worth!
i went to item.cfg i delted the whole line of the noted item and its not working
i look at my armadyl helmet i see 50000 750000 0 0 0 0 0
now when i alch armadyl i get more then 750000 and 50000 i get like 100m.
is there a way to remove noted items or like to fix this?

item.title: How do i change ALCHEMING item prices!
item.dc:creator: @Svitkona Svitkona
item.description:
@Svitkona wrote:

Noted items are the item’s ID +1
so for example, if your armadyl helmet is 9998, if you want it to be noted it will be 9999
